    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "不是，Pending有两个出口：收到payment_received就转到Confirmed，如果超时了就Cancelled。另外客户下单后也可以主动取消。",
