    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把主链路画出来：Pending到Confirmed是payment_received，Pending到Cancelled是timeout。然后Confirmed也能customer_cancel到Cancelled对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Pending",
